Day 21 of #circuitbreaker: The siblings have more time to play now & instead of gadgets, I made use of recycled materials to make a Snack Transporter Game :) The winner gets to eat the @loacker_singapore wafers! ⁣
⁣
How about you? Let me know in the comments what did you "Stay home to _______", and stand a chance to win some Loacker wafers! 2 winners with the most creative / meaningful answer in the post comments will WIN a hamper each 🥰⁣
⁣
⁣
#Stayhome #Loacker #Loackersg #PureGoodness #Quadratini #Wafers #Napolitaner #Cremkakao #igsg #sgfaves #sp #sggiveaway
u should win! so creative babe

Stay home to train my level of multi tasking and patience, wfh with 4 young kids without any help is no joke. Needs lots of yummy snacks to keep them occupied. P.s. Neighbour downstairs has already came up a couple of times 😂😂
Hahahaha your boy so cute!!! 😂😂😂
so cute!!!
Stay home to rejuvenate! Do the things I love, slow down my pace and recharge for a longer journey! Also, to learn to cook / bake more delicious food😍😍
Stay Home to observe their simple laughters, jokes and playtime, which I’ve not had this amount of time last time.
Love the challenge
So sweet that your kids pose for u!!
Hahaha this is so cute!! 🤭
Haha such a fun game and helps kill boredom!
Stay home to indulge in Loacker Wafers, if not the government will lock all of us up LOL! Stay strong together and never waver! 🙌🙌🙌

Stay home to stay safe and save lives! There is nothing like staying at home for real comfort. Home is where we feel loved, appreciated and safe. It is important to stay away from others when possible, even if we do not have symptoms. It's great to spend quality time with my beloved family. The times I feel most loved are the times I'm near family. The love of family can never be replaced, it's one-of-a-kind. I get to bake cookies with my kids. I get to play interesting games with them! We share stories before bedtime. It's great! Keep calm and stay at home, everyone! Hope to win a Loacker hamper to enjoy the moment! My grandkids will love it! Of course, my heart goes to the victims of the tragic event! I hope everyone is doing well! I would like to thank the front liners for their great effort and sacrifice. THANK YOU!

Stay home to stay safe! Here is our only chance to be a superhero just by staying at home. Enjoy quarantine time! The best way to stay safe in these times of crisis is to stay at home. Being at home is the ultimate luxury. Happiness is staying at home. I love spending time with my family and dogs! I help my mum to cook delicious meals and do some cleaning. I would like to win Loacker hamper to share with my family. Stay safe, everyone!

Stay home to bake with Mom! My mother is a good baker and a great mentor. From pineapple tarts at Chinese New Year to gingerbread men at Christmas, it is our festive tradition, and also a great bonding activity. Baking can be a tedious, labour-intensive process, but also an enriching experience for me. My mother shared her secret tips to make her cakes taste better. She takes an organic culinary approach with no shortcuts. She says that the attention to detail will contribute to the ultimate sensory taste and texture. Through this experience, I also picked up an important life lesson from her – To get the best results, do not take shortcuts. This Mother’s Day, I hope she can rest her battered, covered-in-batter baker hands, take a break from the oven and indulge in @loacker_singapore , which makes a great topping/filling for cakes, cookies and tarts! 👩🏻‍🍳👩‍👧‍👦❤️
Very creative. Helps so much with problem solving and thinking out side of the box....or in this case packet. Haha 🤗
stay at home to enjoy quality time with our family that we hardly get when things resume to full speed!  of course that includes snacking together 😂

Stay home to eat together with my family 😍 I love to sit down to have a meal together with my family. A relaxing meal that allows us to have meaningful conversations. Spending quality time with family is important and it goes a long way in boosting happiness. As I get older, the time i spend with my family seems to diminish. Don’t overlook this important area in life because nothing can replace the time spend with family ❤️
stay home to spend quality time with my family & bake/ cook for them because i didn’t have the time to do that before circuit breaker ❤️
Love this snack

I STAY HOME TO shower love upon myself 💯💯💯and to take care of my own mental, physical and emotional well-being. As much as we are affected by the environment around us, we should take the time at home to discover ourselves and the things we like doing, and to reflect on the things we are thankful for 🙌🙌🙌

Stay home to catch up on sleep.. Was so busy at work previously and I finally have time to repay my sleep debts.. hope my dark rings at my eyes will be gone soon 💪 Some chocolate wafer will definitely sweeten my life 😉
@shellisyl congrats!! U are our winner!! Pls DM me ur name, mailing add & number for delivery 😋
@aliciacho thank you!!! 😍
This looks so fun! I stay home to bake for my baby so we can have high tea together with me indulging in my favourite hazelnut Loacker cookies!
Stay home to fill my home with the smell of cake 👍
Stay home to spend more quality time with my loves ones 😘 yay munching Loacker and watching drama show ! ❤🍻 Cheers 🥨
